description: Printing on wooden blocks creates a unique, organic photo that standsthe test of time and gives your image a special effect. With this process, your image fuses with the wood, and you see the grain through the ink. No two prints are alike due to the revealed grain. Whether you want to make your image stand out in a gallery full of other photos, give a one-of-a-kind gift to someone or simply display an eye-catching picture on your wall, wood prints are an excellent way to do it.
